# Reference data (PDFs, DBC files, vendor docs — large binaries, not committed).
# Whitelist below: small JSONs the Docker entrypoint seeders + K-bus calculator
# read at build/runtime — must be in git so a fresh clone (e.g. on Linux) can
# build the standalone image without external state.
# Use `data/*` (not `data/`) so re-include patterns below take effect.
data/*
!data/wago/
data/wago/*
!data/wago/wago_modules.json
!data/commissioning/
data/commissioning/*
!data/commissioning/README.md
!data/commissioning/wago_module_commissioning.json
!data/kbus/
data/kbus/*
!data/kbus/README.md
!data/kbus/kbus_module_costs.json

# Project-specific analysis docs (not source code)
claude_project_handoff.md
lasse_maja_mias_technical_document.md

# Ephemeral inbox-watcher state (FR-006)
staging/

